#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Udāyivagga"
msgstr "3. With Udāyī"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 27. Taṇhānirodhasutta → nirodhasuttaṃ (bj) | nirodho (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Taṇhānirodhasutta"
msgstr "27. The Cessation of Craving"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.27:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo, bhikkhave, maggo yā paṭipadā taṇhānirodhāya saṃvattati, taṃ maggaṃ taṃ "
"paṭipadaṃ bhāvetha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, you should develop the path and the practice that leads to the "
"cessation of craving."

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.2"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, maggo katamā ca paṭipadā taṇhānirodhāya saṃvattati?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the path and the practice that leads to the cessation of craving?"

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.3"
msgid "Yadidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.4"
msgid "satta bojjhaṅgā."
msgstr "It is the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.5"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.6"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo."
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.27:1.7"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā kathaṃ bahulīkatā "
"taṇhānirodhāya saṃvattanti?"
msgstr ""
"And how are the seven awakening factors developed and cultivated so as to "
"lead to the cessation of craving?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.27:2.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "sn46.27:2.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā taṇhānirodhāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is how the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated so as "
"to lead to the cessation of craving.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.27:2.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
